Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.84,0:00:34.47,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,早苗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.30,0:00:37.18,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,这个给你
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.55,0:00:40.93,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,什么啊 是情书吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.97,0:00:43.56,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,才不是 这是普通的信而已
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.64,0:00:45.40,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,大家现在不都这样玩吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.40,0:00:46.27,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你不知道吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.81,0:00:47.65,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.94,0:00:49.02,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.23,0:00:51.78,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,待会我也给由加莉写一封
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.78,0:00:53.19,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你的好意我心领了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.19,0:00:55.82,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,但上课的时候要认真听课啊 美奈
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.82,0:00:58.20,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,比起学习 还是友情比较重要吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.70,0:01:01.66,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,最近女生之间流行写信吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.95,0:01:03.33,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,好像是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.54,0:01:05.92,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,说不定也有在写情书呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.17,0:01:09.46,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,她们写什么都很认真的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.79,0:01:11.13,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,谁知道呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.13,0:01:12.67,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,情书吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.67,0:01:15.47,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,直接用嘴说就好了 居然还特意写在纸上
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.47,0:01:17.64,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,她们还真不嫌麻烦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.68,0:01:19.55,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,看来她们挺闲的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.81,0:01:28.86,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,{\an8}对不起对不起对不起…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.15,0:01:31.23,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,等等 早苗 你干得太过了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.69,0:01:33.36,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,一下就够了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.61,0:01:35.82,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,还是要踢一脚啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.74,0:01:39.37,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,开始上课了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.91,0:01:42.66,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,翻到课本76页
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.12,0:01:50.63,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,高木同学也在写信吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.34,0:01:56.42,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,说到底高木同学也只是个普通的女生而已嘛
Comment: 0,0:00:00.43,0:00:00.43,Default,,0,0,0,,——op——
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.37,0:03:45.62,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,信
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.46,0:03:53.92,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你怎么了 西片
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.42,0:03:56.79,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.34,0:03:59.42,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,是信 谁送来的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.46,0:04:01.13,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,为什么要写给我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.17,0:04:03.47,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,说不定也有在写情书呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.84,0:04:06.47,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不不不不 这怎么可能
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.55,0:04:08.06,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,肯定是谁的恶作剧…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.56,0:04:10.06,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,对了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.52,0:04:14.35,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,这说不定是高木同学的恶作剧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.35,0:04:16.11,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不 肯定是这样的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.86,0:04:19.11,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,高木同学…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.53,0:04:22.24,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,等等 要是弄错了该怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.24,0:04:23.70,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,要不是高木同学写的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.99,0:04:25.74,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,一旦我收到信件的事情暴露了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.74,0:04:27.70,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,肯定又会被高木同学捉弄的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.58,0:04:29.95,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,怎么了 西片
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.66,0:04:33.04,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,这个…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.42,0:04:40.71,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,今天天气不错啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.01,0:04:42.47,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,是不是在瞒着什么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.67,0:04:45.43,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,怎么可能
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.60,0:04:49.97,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,但感觉你好可疑哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.52,0:04:51.72,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,脸还那么红
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.60,0:04:54.02,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,是你的错觉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.39,0:04:55.90,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,是错觉就好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.19,0:04:57.73,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你为什么不翻开课本
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.81,0:05:00.61,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,这个嘛…那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.15,0:05:03.61,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,这和你脸红有关系吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.74,0:05:06.24,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,没有 我的脸也没有红
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.95,0:05:08.62,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,真的没事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.74,0:05:10.74,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,都说了什么事也没有
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.12,0:05:16.08,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,是我的错觉吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.58,0:05:21.05,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,还有 夹在书里的那封信
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.55,0:05:22.76,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,是我放的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.84,0:05:27.64,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,果然是她干的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.60,0:05:33.98,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,这种把戏 我完全看穿了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.14,0:05:36.19,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你撒谎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.69,0:05:40.27,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我只是装不知道而已
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.90,0:05:42.73,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你不看看里面写了什么吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.78,0:05:44.61,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,什么 里面写了东西吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.28,0:05:46.57,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,肯定啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.16,0:05:51.99,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,反正又是捉弄我的内容吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.16,0:05:57.00,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你干嘛不说话
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.17,0:06:01.09,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,那既然你写了 我就看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.79,0:06:03.21,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你现在看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.21,0:06:05.63,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.01,0:06:08.84,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,因为这节课下课之后就放学了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.22,0:06:10.89,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,想你在那之前答复我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.93,0:06:12.64,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,答 答复？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.06,0:06:19.60,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,需要作出回复的信件 也就是说里面有提问
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.85,0:06:22.90,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,内容难道不只是恶作剧吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.32,0:06:25.65,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,说不定也有在写情书呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.57,0:06:29.32,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,也就是说有可能是情书吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.49,0:06:31.32,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不 不会吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.33,0:06:37.54,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,难道是情书什么的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.50,0:06:42.00,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,又默不出声吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.38,0:06:43.67,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你不看看吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.05,0:06:46.42,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我看 我会看的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.42,0:06:48.55,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,看了就行吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.92,0:06:53.89,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,照那么说 里面写的肯定是恶作剧之类的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.93,0:06:56.72,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,那无论里面写了什么 我都要保持镇定不被她捉弄到
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.85,0:06:59.39,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,堂堂正正地
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.31,0:07:01.48,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.73,0:07:02.90,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,要是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.23,0:07:06.94,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,虽然肯定是不可能的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.61,0:07:09.95,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,但要真是情书的话
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.36,0:07:14.16,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我该…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.66,0:07:23.58,Takagisan-huamian,,0,0,0,,{\fs100\fad(200,0)\frx8\fry0\frz352.3\move(641.6,408,643.2,308.8,195,4908)}给西片
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.66,0:07:23.58,Takagisan-huamian,,0,0,0,,{\fs100\frz345.8\frx2\fry4\move(657.6,917.2,660.8,840.4,195,4908)\fad(200,0)}今天一起回家吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.01,0:07:37.39,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,直接跟我说不就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.52,0:07:39.43,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,现在流行写信嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.64,0:07:45.56,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,而且 我也想看看你会有怎样的反应
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.32,0:07:50.44,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你果然是在捉弄我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.44,0:07:51.32,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,好疼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.49,0:07:54.28,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,吵死了 西片
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.67,0:08:10.26,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,入学典礼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.35,0:08:20.60,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,哎呀 麻烦你专门跑一趟了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.73,0:08:22.52,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,没什么 我先告辞了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.98,0:08:24.98,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,对了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.81,0:08:28.77,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,新生 你的名字叫什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.40,0:08:30.65,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,您问我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.49,0:08:32.78,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我叫西片
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.90,0:08:36.53,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,西片 祝贺你入学
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.99,0:08:41.45,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.16,0:08:46.38,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,在接下来的一年里 你们就是一起学习的伙伴了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.88,0:08:49.21,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我不会要求你们每时每刻都保持融洽
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.50,0:08:53.22,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,但希望你们尽可能和谐相处
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.67,0:08:55.84,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,是掉到哪里去了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.68,0:09:00.18,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,嘛 刚开学也没有什么需要唠叨的…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.39,0:09:04.19,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,突然就来了个睡过头的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.35,0:09:06.19,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不是 那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.23,0:09:08.65,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你的胆量我倒是挺佩服
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.98,0:09:10.02,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.02,0:09:11.15,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你叫什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.40,0:09:14.03,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我叫西片
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.45,0:09:16.57,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,算了 坐下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.03,0:09:18.49,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.46,0:09:26.71,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,好显眼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.79,0:09:29.34,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,在被定性为迟到型角色之前
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.34,0:09:32.30,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,得赶紧和大家打好交道 解开误会才行
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.22,0:09:37.76,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,田边老师 能打扰一下吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.72,0:09:42.01,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,车子好像晚点才到
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.47,0:09:44.60,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,迟到了吗 那仪式也要推迟吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.89,0:09:46.56,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.52,0:09:50.94,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,现在入学典礼的准备时间延长了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.98,0:09:53.40,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,好像会耽搁不少时间
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.61,0:09:55.07,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,在这期间
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.03,0:09:58.61,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我们来决定座位顺序
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.91,0:10:07.46,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,怎么会这样
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.46,0:10:10.58,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,偏偏抽到了最后一排最角落的位置
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.92,0:10:12.67,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,放在平时会是件令人高兴的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.67,0:10:14.96,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,但对现在的我来说只有坏处
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.13,0:10:17.34,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,本来就一个人也不认识
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.80,0:10:20.72,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,现在左边和后面都没有人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.89,0:10:23.35,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,而且旁边坐的还是女生
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.35,0:10:27.02,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你真的睡过头了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.39,0:10:30.06,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,她向我搭话了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.06,0:10:32.23,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,因为老师好像跟你说了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.07,0:10:37.07,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,该怎么说好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.15,0:10:39.86,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,要是没有迟到的话
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.95,0:10:42.45,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我都明明准时到学校了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.33,0:10:46.12,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,都怪一个叫高木同学的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.00,0:10:50.29,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,好 所有人去体育馆
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.79,0:10:53.17,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,安静一点 不要跑
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.25,0:10:54.80,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.34,0:11:00.26,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我说 一起去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.30,0:11:02.72,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.77,0:11:08.73,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,难道说…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.98,0:11:15.86,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你们总有一天会得到选举权这笔无价的财富
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.94,0:11:21.16,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,最重要的是要选择值得信赖的政治家
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.41,0:11:25.95,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,请务必 让爸爸和妈妈…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.66,0:11:30.79,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,演讲太长了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.79,0:11:31.29,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,就是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.46,0:11:33.96,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,大叔的演讲就是长
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.25,0:11:37.17,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,无论在小学还是中学都没什么变化嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.71,0:11:41.43,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不过开学第一天就迟到 你也是厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.97,0:11:42.97,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,这个嘛…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.05,0:11:44.97,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不要吵了 回到座位上
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.39,0:11:52.90,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.98,0:11:58.65,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,抱歉 我迟到了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.61,0:12:00.82,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,快点坐下
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.74,0:12:05.82,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,今天就到此结束了 明天开始正式上课
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.82,0:12:09.24,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不要因为是开学典礼就得意忘形 要乖乖回家啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.91,0:12:11.79,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我说 西片
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.00,0:12:17.46,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我来猜猜今天西片迟到的理由吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.67,0:12:21.34,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,要是一次就猜中 那就算我赢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.97,0:12:23.26,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,可以啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.05,0:12:26.80,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,一次是猜不中的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.43,0:12:31.68,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,是去送还失物了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.81,0:12:33.56,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,诶 为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.60,0:12:35.60,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,喂 你太吵了西片
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.15,0:12:37.52,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.44,0:12:41.90,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,为什么你会知道
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.87,0:12:49.74,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,为什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.79,0:12:57.08,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,高木同学？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.21,0:12:59.92,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,做自我介绍的时候你不在呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.05,0:13:10.39,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你的反应是怎么回事啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.51,0:13:12.56,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我说 那一块很吵啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.98,0:13:14.39,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.36,0:13:24.57,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,谢谢你帮我捡回来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.32,0:13:29.20,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,以后请多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.87,0:13:34.96,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,请多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.17,0:13:37.96,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,换座位
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.00,0:13:43.09,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,七十二 七十三
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.67,0:13:49.51,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,七十四 七十五
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.02,0:13:58.31,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,有点肌肉了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.86,0:14:12.20,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,好疼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.73,0:14:41.90,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,她还没来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.11,0:14:46.28,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,早上好 西片
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.94,0:14:49.03,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,早上好 高木同学
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.41,0:14:54.28,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你知道吗 西片
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.83,0:14:58.00,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,今天要换座位
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.00,0:15:05.67,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,什么时候
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.92,0:15:07.09,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,班会课的时候换
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.13,0:15:10.30,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,班会课不是第一节吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.52,0:15:24.52,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,{\an8}高木同学…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.52,0:15:24.52,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.40,0:15:30.70,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,原来是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.07,0:15:32.16,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,好期待啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.24,0:15:34.53,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.29,0:15:39.41,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,因为 好久没有换过座位了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.46,0:15:50.09,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,虽然也有值得期待的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.18,0:15:55.14,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,但我还是觉得西片旁边的位置比较好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.97,0:16:01.35,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,她又要捉弄我了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.06,0:16:04.02,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,好险啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.29,0:16:21.29,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,所有人都抽签了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.66,0:16:25.33,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,好 按签上面写的调换座位吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.92,0:16:27.29,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,西片是多少号
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.50,0:16:28.75,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,29号
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.92,0:16:32.84,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,这样啊 又是在最后一排呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.05,0:16:34.01,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,高木同学呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.05,0:16:38.22,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我在中间那列的第一位
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.72,0:16:40.10,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.89,0:16:43.48,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我们离得好远啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.56,0:16:46.56,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,再见了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.23,0:16:49.78,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.82,0:16:52.44,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,由加莉 考试的时候告诉我答案吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.44,0:16:54.57,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不对 一般来说那算抄袭了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.66,0:16:56.16,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,是相互帮助啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.16,0:16:58.08,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,美奈要怎么帮我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.08,0:16:59.91,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我从后面给你加油
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.83,0:17:03.04,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,哟 西片
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.21,0:17:04.62,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你坐这里吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.67,0:17:05.75,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不 是对面
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.08,0:17:09.46,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,这样啊 要是在附近就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.54,0:17:10.55,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,就是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.47,0:17:17.89,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我最近视力变差了 不知道能不能看清黑板呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.95,0:17:37.99,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,旁边坐的原来是西片啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.03,0:17:40.28,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,真野同学
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.37,0:17:42.45,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,啊 是这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.83,0:17:47.12,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,怎么了 你这反应
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.58,0:17:50.84,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,没什么 不要介意
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.30,0:17:56.76,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,只是不能和中井坐到一块 有点失落而已
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.72,0:18:02.97,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,中井的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.81,0:18:06.18,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,有谁吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.73,0:18:09.52,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,有谁能和我换换座位吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.77,0:18:13.48,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,坐着讲台的正前方 我要怎么偷吃午饭啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.65,0:18:16.90,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,没有正当理由的话 不可以换座位
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.28,0:18:20.45,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,还有木村 你跟我来教员室一趟
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.91,0:18:22.12,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.04,0:18:24.83,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,讲台正前方
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.75,0:18:29.50,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我觉得还是西片旁边的位置比较好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.35,0:18:48.56,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,木村
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.56,0:18:50.56,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我视力不太好 我们交换吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.90,0:18:53.94,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不行 我已经换好了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.74,0:19:05.08,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,无所谓了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.25,0:19:10.29,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,西片
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.08,0:19:11.79,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.09,0:19:22.09,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.89,0:19:25.06,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我把座位换到这里了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.10,0:19:26.43,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,诶 为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.10,0:19:31.69,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我让中井同学和木村同学以看不见黑板为由换了座位
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.19,0:19:34.19,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,因为中井坐到了最前面
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.27,0:19:37.94,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,原本坐他旁边的我就和真野换了位置
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.24,0:19:41.41,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,因为真野个子小 坐前面比较好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.91,0:19:43.91,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,原来是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.20,0:19:48.79,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,西片 你原本打算换到我旁边的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.75,0:19:55.54,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,那个 因为我看不清黑板
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.80,0:19:59.17,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.22,0:20:05.72,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我说真的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.05,0:20:07.64,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,开始上课了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.76,0:20:08.97,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,把课本拿出来
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.56,0:20:10.52,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,啊 对了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.73,0:20:12.64,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,西片想跟我说什么来着
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.81,0:20:17.15,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,从早上开始 你就一直想和我说些什么似的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.78,0:20:28.20,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,这个 抱歉还晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.41,0:20:29.74,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.50,0:20:31.96,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,是暑假那时的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.16,0:20:33.37,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.83,0:20:35.13,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,还有
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.54,0:20:37.04,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,入学典礼那天的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.34,0:20:38.34,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你还记得啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.67,0:20:40.96,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,西片才是 亏你还记得啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.88,0:20:44.34,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.39,0:20:47.05,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.76,0:20:49.47,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我把它洗干净了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.90,0:20:55.98,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.40,0:20:58.32,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不过 太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.86,0:21:02.15,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我是指各种事情
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.36,0:21:04.53,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,比如把手帕还给你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.70,0:21:06.95,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,又能一起坐什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.49,0:21:09.66,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,那个…各种事情
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.16,0:21:12.70,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,以后也请多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.08,0:21:14.00,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,{\an8}I do not say
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.33,0:21:15.29,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.54,0:21:17.71,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,{\an8}在这篇文章里 do是一般现在时
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.75,0:21:22.26,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,{\an8}这时把它变成过去式的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.95,0:21:48.16,Takagisan-huamian-1,,0,0,0,,{\frz270\fs180\pos(1098,310)}给高木同学
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.95,0:21:48.16,Takagisan-huamian-1,,0,0,0,,{\frz270\fs180\pos(720,494)}非常感谢
